  <h2>Rails: Serving the long tail in 1883 and 2005</h2>
  <p class="auth">Posted by kev
  <span class="typo_date" title="Sun, 16 Oct 2005 21:56:25 GMT">Sun, 16 Oct 2005 21:56:25 GMT</span></p>
  <div id="adsense">
  <script type="text/javascript"><!--
google_ad_client = "pub-1730274975094059";
google_ad_width = 468;
google_ad_height = 60;
google_ad_format = "468x60_as";
